# Requires: i3 polybar xss-lock betterlockscreen ttf-jetbrains-mono-nerd ttf-gohu-nerd ttf-0xproto-nerd nano-syntax-highlighting picom dmenu rofi feh maim brightnessctl kitty firefox lxqt-policykit networkmanager network-manager-applet wpa_supplicant thunar xautolock pipewire wireplumber pipewire-pulse pactl visual-studio-code-bin

